==Rackspace Cloud Helper Files==

*Description:*
A collection of little helpful code snippets for dealing with RackSpace Cloud

*Requirements:*
Varies from file to file, but generally PHP, CURL, PHP5-CURL, PECL, and of course the Rackspace Cloud Files PHP binding, which you can get from GitHub

*Originally Released:*
September 20, 2012

*Credits:*
Written by Brooke Schreier Ganz (asparagirl -at- dca -dot- net / Twitter: @Asparagirl).  Some of the thumbnail generation script is based on other freely available code.

*License:*
Freedom Isn't Free, but these files are.  Use them in good health, as my grandma would say.
